{"tid":1392394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工處推網上職安健投訴平台","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T23:03:26.000Z","uid":206097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df0c974e9a015ed8675a6ff7e59054f7ad7096fb","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"勞工處今日推出網上職業安全及健康投訴平台，市民可利用電子表格舉報工作地點的不安全作業模式或環境。<br />\n <br />\n勞工處表示，網上平台有助處方盡快跟進職安健不當作業的投訴，派員巡視相關工作地點，防止意外發生。<br />\n <br />\n除了網上平台，市民仍可通過電郵、致電熱線2542 2172或1823舉報。"},{"pid":"c1b4e80a84fdc12087697a9bb47959f7c5569dde","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47294917795d6d3a663ffe19db4144ab7a3500e","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c058cf4addae4b24916f037494bd508234b8e6e6","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f35357ca61ddb08cb93a88894954d56560784db","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377758e99cf91d7ec3366dc172cda77d325a3941","tid":1392394,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}